    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with clinical syndromes or situations at increased risk of cardiac
             arrhythmias

          -  Patients who experience transient symptoms that may suggest a cardiac arrhythmia

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients that have had a myocardial infarction (MI) &lt; 30 days prior to implant
      </textblock>
